<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[بَذِير]</span>: رجل بَذِيرٌ: لا يكتم السرّ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>و <span class="c4">[بَذيّ]</span>: رجل بَذِيّ اللسان.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>... و <span class="c4">[فعيلة]</span>، بالهاء<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[همزة]</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[بَذِيئَة]</span>: أرضَ بذِيئَةٌ: لا مرعى بها.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>... فُعُلّى، بضم الفاء والعين وتشديد اللام<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
